{"tid":2077901,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【拋豬引肉】作咗首抗爭紀念歌 有無人可以幫手改名","createTime":"2020-06-24T15:38:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T16:17:04.000Z","uid":270286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"90ae174862276c5e57ad24db2207db62446c52e8","tid":2077901,"uid":270286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T15:38:15.000Z","msg":"首歌其實舊年9月已經開始寫，最近完成咗鋼琴錄音同埋填咗少少詞，希望大家可以畀啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下係歌詞MV (劣整勿插）:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NL6XtwBhxZI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNL6XtwBhxZI&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPpKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=3c8399c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NL6XtwBhxZI</a><br />\n<br />\n純伴奏音樂：<br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/azm-hk/x-1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fazm-hk%2Fx-1&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPpKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=1dfbd6cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/azm-hk/x-1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歌詞：<br />\n<br />\n齊聲高歌&nbsp;唱出光明<br />\n前進鬥志&nbsp;永不熄滅<br />\n喚醒香港&nbsp;跨世代團結<br />\n勇武對抗&nbsp;嗜血極權<br />\n<br />\n誰敢攬炒&nbsp;捍守尊嚴<br />\n誰戴上眼罩&nbsp;復光家園<br />\n頭盔扑穿&nbsp;千里路踏破<br />\n智慧似劍&nbsp;憤義似火<br />\n<br />\n任&nbsp;希望飄渺<br />\n夢裡&nbsp;挽手思革命<br />\n問&nbsp;如何能夠&nbsp;全城同奏<br />\n拋開榮辱搏鬥&nbsp;靠信念奮起<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n齊聲高歌&nbsp;唱出光明<br />\n前進鬥志&nbsp;永不熄滅<br />\n並肩獅山&nbsp;風雨共明志<br />\n痛過笑過&nbsp;哪怕動搖<br />\n<br />\n流水開花&nbsp;湧出清泉<br />\n傳說過去&nbsp;這個夏天<br />\n願今生&nbsp;終可煲底相見<br />\n無悔依個時代碰見<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n寫依首歌嘅時候有幾個諗法&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n1.&nbsp;希望將值得香港人驕傲嘅事件同圖騰擺落歌詞度；<br />\n<br />\n2. 用粵語入文；<br />\n<br />\n3.&nbsp;以光明、正面嘅歌詞同正氣既旋律，提升同路人嘅士氣，迎向勝利之日。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家聽完之後可以畀啲意見，小弟一個人能力有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無論係歌名、歌詞、編曲、唱，都好需要大家幫忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n抗爭至今已經超過一年，或者當初根本無人知道我地可以堅持到今日。希望依首歌可以幫大家回憶過去一年我地所經歷嘅事、記得每一位手足嘅付出、記得我地嘅初衷，一齊堅持落去，直至煲底相見！"},{"pid":"31cbe40468450df6ebc564c0290851c63f722ea6","tid":2077901,"uid":270286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T15:41:15.000Z","msg":"P牌仔推唔到都照自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d06db1d314ca071ee953d8e8182fdede0820d3","tid":2077901,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T15:42:15.000Z","msg":"無人唱既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96fcdb7bf456a644de2553af48ce84d4a6a89a16","tid":2077901,"uid":270286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59d06db1d314ca071ee953d8e8182fdede0820d3","tid":2077901,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T15:42:15.000Z","msg":"無人唱既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T17:16:33.000Z","msg":"有無巴絲幫手唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"779369a2a3f786a36ed6aa9df3cc793916ebc23a","tid":2077901,"uid":270286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T16:17:04.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}